Sets the vibration of controller specified by ''controllerID''
BEGIN EX

		function OnGUI() {
			PS3Pad.SetVibration (0, true, 0.2);
		}
END EX
@param controllerID Controller index
@param smallMotor true to enable the small motor and false to disable it
@param bigMotor 0.0 - 1.0 where 0.0 is motor off and 1.0 is motor at maximum
@return @@true@@ if the enable to change the motor settings otherwise @@false@@ This might occur if controller doesn't support vibration